        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. Megophrys frigida sp. nov. in preservative: (a) dorsal view (holotype of VNMN 010948); (b) ventral view (holotype of VNMN 010948); (c) lateral view of head (holotype of VNMN 010948); (d) palmar surface of left hand (holotype of VNMN 010948); (e) plantar surface of left foot (holotype of VNMN 010948); (f, g, h) dorsal, ventral and profile view of Megophrys frigida sp. nov. paratype (AMS R186131). Scale bars: 10 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5029441/files/figure.png" .

